{"tid":746376,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【天地會咩？】網傳碧桂園員工集體飲雞血谷銷售","createTime":"2018-07-17T13:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:58:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"364f948485fda0615ea97c4ad90000c89162bac1","tid":746376,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180716/large/1531749179_2b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180716%2Flarge%2F1531749179_2b4e.jpg&h=9210a3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳碧桂園放雞血給員工喝。(網絡圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180716/large/1531749197_54db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180716%2Flarge%2F1531749197_54db.jpg&h=46cb513f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似碧桂園員工將雞血一飲而盡。(網絡圖片)<br />\n<br />\n碧桂園（2007）傳出暫緩投地、叫停三四五線城市「全覆蓋」戰略等等，壞消息不斷。公司否認全面叫停，但承認退出部分合作非操盤項目。中國房地政策趨緊，員工都要盡力幫公司套現。<br />\n<br />\n今日在微博就傳出相片，指碧桂園福建省漳州市御江府開誓師大會，員工集體喝雞血，以振奮士氣。網友就留言「傳播禽流感」、「病態的行業、病態的單位」、「不是雞血，房地產喝的是人血！」惟公司未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n在中國，「打雞血」為在文化大革命年代曾是瘋狂蔓延的一種「保健療法」，網路上被衍生的意思為瘋狂的行為，亦被用來形容一個人特別興奮。<br />\n<br />\n碧桂園今日收報12.74元，跌2.1%。"},{"pid":"4cd31b5d3bfdda5dad5b86f2b212bea0c1f7b1bf","tid":746376,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"由上到下都<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該就快出義和拳2.0"},{"pid":"dee354b3acffbebbe1242ca1cb6d2fb1e7941cb4","tid":746376,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"生番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c56380ac1d721ec88294672dab0e1e5b8f49d00","tid":746376,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dee354b3acffbebbe1242ca1cb